snippet.title: HiveDive - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
An on-rail shooter where you pilot a remote-controlled drone into hordes of enemies. Shoot down the invaders and fly through colorful Patagonia.

Hive Dive is a student project by 3rd year university students at Breda University of Applied Sciences.
